  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Field of Honor is a singleplayer, blend of first-person shooter and strategic warfare set amidst the gripping backdrop of Napoleonic Wars, American Revolutionary War and American Civil War.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >First Person Gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare to be a foot soldier or cavalry in AI controlled battles. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2606920/extras/ee7d93c6794a1b3646c4c0a3b863a1db.poster.avif?t=1766596512\" width=600 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2606920/extras/ee7d93c6794a1b3646c4c0a3b863a1db.webm?t=1766596512\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2606920/extras/ee7d93c6794a1b3646c4c0a3b863a1db.mp4?t=1766596512\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2606920/extras/a4af1426d95a95ab0dfe278511f1e8b0.poster.avif?t=1766596512\" width=600 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2606920/extras/a4af1426d95a95ab0dfe278511f1e8b0.webm?t=1766596512\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2606920/extras/a4af1426d95a95ab0dfe278511f1e8b0.mp4?t=1766596512\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Strategy Gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Command your army in first person or directly on strategy map.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2606920/extras/79e88b692690952746c6fccc5269267b.poster.avif?t=1766596512\" width=600 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2606920/extras/79e88b692690952746c6fccc5269267b.webm?t=1766596512\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2606920/extras/79e88b692690952746c6fccc5269267b.mp4?t=1766596512\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Big Scale</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Field of Honor brings to life the epic clashes of the past, featuring breathtaking engagements with over 1000+ units on the battlefield simultaneously. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2606920/extras/5abdea26d6f81601ca57dd7302f799ac.poster.avif?t=1766596512\" width=600 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2606920/extras/5abdea26d6f81601ca57dd7302f799ac.webm?t=1766596512\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2606920/extras/5abdea26d6f81601ca57dd7302f799ac.mp4?t=1766596512\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Napoleonic Wars Nations:</strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play with France, Austria, Prussia, Great Britain, Russia, Spain, Sweden, Portugal, Kingdom of Italy, Ottoman Empire, Duchy of Warsaw, United States, Bavaria , Kingdom of Naples, Duchy of Nassau, Swiss Confederation, Kingdom of Holland, Denmark-Norway and Westphalia.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2606920/extras/8ebebfef45b2a6b692acdd50f1120664.avif?t=1766596512\" width=600 height=334 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>American Revolutionary War Nations:</strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play with revolutionary era United States or Great Britain.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2606920/extras/2a4ab4a56d8b0054eaf57e2ab586a524.avif?t=1766596512\" width=262 height=86 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>American CivilWar Nations:</strong>   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play with civil war era Union or Confederate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Different Units:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each nations has its own units in 3 different category; Artillery, Cavalry and Infantry.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Command on Map:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Command your army corps over command map easily.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Command in FPS:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can also control units with FPS view and make them to charge, attack or move etc.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Meelee Combat</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take up your sword and command a bayonet charge!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>AI Commander:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enemy is commanded by AI. Also you can leave friendly units comanded by AI and just fight as a single soldier in massive battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>4 Different Mods:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play in Conquest, Defense, Assault and Custom Battle modes for immerse different gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Roadmap</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Field of Honor is developed as Earcly Access game. So there is more to come. We plan make updates in montly period. Key features that we plan to add are:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New nations of Napoleonic wars.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New units for each nation.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cannon, rocket and other tools control</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New missile and melee weapons</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Field of Honor is a singleplayer, blend of first-person shooter and strategic warfare set amidst the gripping backdrop of Napoleonic Wars, American Revolutionary War and American Civil War.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >First Person Gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare to be a foot soldier or cavalry in AI controlled battles. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2606920/extras/ee7d93c6794a1b3646c4c0a3b863a1db.poster.avif?t=1766596512\" width=600 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2606920/extras/ee7d93c6794a1b3646c4c0a3b863a1db.webm?t=1766596512\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2606920/extras/ee7d93c6794a1b3646c4c0a3b863a1db.mp4?t=1766596512\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2606920/extras/a4af1426d95a95ab0dfe278511f1e8b0.poster.avif?t=1766596512\" width=600 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2606920/extras/a4af1426d95a95ab0dfe278511f1e8b0.webm?t=1766596512\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2606920/extras/a4af1426d95a95ab0dfe278511f1e8b0.mp4?t=1766596512\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Strategy Gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Command your army in first person or directly on strategy map.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2606920/extras/79e88b692690952746c6fccc5269267b.poster.avif?t=1766596512\" width=600 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2606920/extras/79e88b692690952746c6fccc5269267b.webm?t=1766596512\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2606920/extras/79e88b692690952746c6fccc5269267b.mp4?t=1766596512\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Big Scale</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Field of Honor brings to life the epic clashes of the past, featuring breathtaking engagements with over 1000+ units on the battlefield simultaneously. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2606920/extras/5abdea26d6f81601ca57dd7302f799ac.poster.avif?t=1766596512\" width=600 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2606920/extras/5abdea26d6f81601ca57dd7302f799ac.webm?t=1766596512\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2606920/extras/5abdea26d6f81601ca57dd7302f799ac.mp4?t=1766596512\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Napoleonic Wars Nations:</strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play with France, Austria, Prussia, Great Britain, Russia, Spain, Sweden, Portugal, Kingdom of Italy, Ottoman Empire, Duchy of Warsaw, United States, Bavaria , Kingdom of Naples, Duchy of Nassau, Swiss Confederation, Kingdom of Holland, Denmark-Norway and Westphalia.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2606920/extras/8ebebfef45b2a6b692acdd50f1120664.avif?t=1766596512\" width=600 height=334 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>American Revolutionary War Nations:</strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play with revolutionary era United States or Great Britain.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2606920/extras/2a4ab4a56d8b0054eaf57e2ab586a524.avif?t=1766596512\" width=262 height=86 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>American CivilWar Nations:</strong>   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play with civil war era Union or Confederate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Different Units:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each nations has its own units in 3 different category; Artillery, Cavalry and Infantry.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Command on Map:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Command your army corps over command map easily.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Command in FPS:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can also control units with FPS view and make them to charge, attack or move etc.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Meelee Combat</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take up your sword and command a bayonet charge!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>AI Commander:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enemy is commanded by AI. Also you can leave friendly units comanded by AI and just fight as a single soldier in massive battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>4 Different Mods:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play in Conquest, Defense, Assault and Custom Battle modes for immerse different gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Roadmap</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Field of Honor is developed as Earcly Access game. So there is more to come. We plan make updates in montly period. Key features that we plan to add are:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New nations of Napoleonic wars.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New units for each nation.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cannon, rocket and other tools control</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New missile and melee weapons</p></li></ul>",
